550
00:32:57,800 --> 00:32:58,960
Kalau rakyat jelata…

551
00:32:59,560 --> 00:33:01,480
ingin membeli barang yang sama,

552
00:33:01,960 --> 00:33:03,360
bukankah miskin seumur hidup pun…

553
00:33:03,600 --> 00:33:04,920
takkan bisa membeli barang asli?

554
00:33:05,960 --> 00:33:08,720
Jadi semua barang imitasimu ini…

555
00:33:09,280 --> 00:33:11,200
kau jual ke rakyat jelata?

556
00:33:11,520 --> 00:33:12,200
Benar sekali.

557
00:33:14,600 --> 00:33:15,640
Tak bisa beli yang asli,

558
00:33:15,800 --> 00:33:16,440
lalu membeli yang palsu.

559
00:33:16,600 --> 00:33:17,440
